OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,FA police helicopter that flew
OL,8,Fextremely low over a field in St
OL,9,FHelens, while chasing what was
OL,10,Fbelieved to be a stolen scrambler
OL,11,Fbike, "acted appropriately" according
OL,12,Fto an internal review.
OL,14,FThe National Police Air Service say
OL,15,Fthey checked the aircraft's camera and
OL,16,Fradio recordings and found the crew
OL,17,Fperformed an "accepted" manoeuvre.
