OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,FNPAS confirmed that footage of the
OL,8,Fflight, widely seen on social media,
OL,9,Fwas from an "operation" near Carr Mill
OL,10,FDam on 13 August.
OL,12,FWitnesses alleged the bike rider was
OL,13,Fspeeding, mounting pavements, and at
OL,14,Fone point came dangerously close to
OL,15,Fhitting a pedestrian. A second man
OL,16,Freportedly joined the rider on the
OL,17,Fbike and was later arrested after
OL,18,Fgetting off.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
