OL,7,FA second suspect was detained for
OL,8,Ftheft of a motor vehicle and assisting
OL,9,Fan offender.
OL,11,FChief Superintendent Fiona Gaffney of
OL,12,FNPAS said: "While the footage has
OL,13,Funderstandably generated public
OL,14,Finterest, it is important to view it
OL,15,Fin the full context of an operation
OL,16,Fthat lasted over an hour.
