OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,F"At around 2.30pm, our air crew was
OL,8,Fdeployed to assist Merseyside Police
OL,9,Ffollowing reports of a man riding a
OL,10,Fscrambler bike in a dangerous and
OL,11,Freckless manner near Carr Mill Dam.
OL,13,F"Our crew tracked the motorcyclist for
OL,14,Fover an hour, providing continuous
OL,15,Fupdates to ground officers. This was a
OL,16,Flegitimate policing task in support of
OL,17,Fpublic safety and crime prevention.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
