OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,F"Once in a safe location, the crew
OL,8,Frecorded the decision to lower
OL,9,Faltitude with the intention of
OL,10,Flanding. As the motorcyclist continued
OL,11,Fto make off, the landing was
OL,12,Fdiscontinued and the aircraft
OL,13,Faccelerated before climbing away. This
OL,14,Fis an accepted take-off manoeuvre.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
