OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,F"Following an internal review of the
OL,8,Faircraft's camera footage, radio
OL,9,Fcommentary and operational decision-
OL,10,Fmaking, we are satisfied that the crew
OL,11,Facted appropriately, conducted a
OL,12,Fdynamic risk assessment and operated
OL,13,Fwithin the parameters and regulations
OL,14,Ffor our operational deployments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
