OL,3,CPolice helicopter 'acted
OL,4,Cappropriately' in bike chase, says
OL,5,Cinternal review
OL,7,F"The fast-paced and unpredictable
OL,8,Fnature of vehicle pursuits can require
OL,9,Fcrews to make rapid decisions to
OL,10,Fensure public safety. We have robust
OL,11,Fprocedures in place to support these
OL,12,Fdecisions and safety remains our
OL,13,Fhighest priority.
OL,15,F"We continue to work closely with the
OL,16,FCivil Aviation Authority to ensure all
OL,17,Frelevant standards and procedures are
OL,18,Fupheld. We thank the public for their
OL,19,Fconcern and engagement and we remain
OL,20,Fcommitted to transparency and
OL,21,Fprofessionalism in all our operations."
